Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.50,0:02:53.08,op-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}許せば進めるし　恨みは立ち止らす
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.08,0:02:58.08,op-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}あれは僕のせいにしな　それも僕のせいにしてよ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.08,0:03:03.20,op-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}君をずっと立ち止めるその全てと
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.20,0:03:08.92,op-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}僕以外を許して進んで行きなよ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.31,0:03:18.36,op-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}生涯枯れることのない花と名付けても
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.36,0:03:23.47,op-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}生涯枯れることのない花になることはない
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.01,0:03:28.58,op-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\3c&HDA7B00&}真面目に生きていればいつか報われる
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.04,0:03:33.62,op-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}そうやって言い切ってしまえばそれは嘘になる
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.62,0:03:38.69,op-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}身に起こるその数十％自業自得でも
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.69,0:03:43.60,op-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}残りの数％誰のせいでもないその不平等
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.60,0:03:53.68,op-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\3c&H1200FF&\t(2560,2810,\3c&H265CF5&)\t(3269,3519,\3c&HDA7B00&)\t(3603,3811,\3c&H47C73E&)\t(3937,4103,\3c&H5F2558&)\t(4437,4562,\3c&H386A2D&)\t(5396,5438,\3c&H1200FF&)\t(6189,6481,\3c&H45B6FE&,\bord0.8)\t(8274,8441,\blur0,\3c&H103568&,\bord2,\1c&HCCE1F4&)\t(8775,9275,\3c&H52164B&)\t(9359,9609,\blur3,\3c&H103568&)}一番いけないことはさ　自分は駄目だと思うこと
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.68,0:03:58.68,op-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}あれは僕のせいにしな　それも僕のせいにしてよ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.68,0:04:03.72,op-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}僕以外を許して進んで行きなよ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.72,0:04:09.29,op-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}君自身のことも許してあげてよ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.72,0:04:09.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.50,0:02:53.08,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}宽恕促人前行 仇恨让人停滞
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.08,0:02:58.08,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}把那个当成我的错吧 把这个也归咎于我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.08,0:03:03.20,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}原谅让你一直停滞不前之事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.20,0:03:08.92,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}原谅除我以外的所有人 前进吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.31,0:03:18.36,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}即便为永不凋谢之花命名
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.36,0:03:23.47,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}也无法永不凋谢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.01,0:03:28.58,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\3c&HDA7B00&}认真活着就会有回报
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.04,0:03:33.62,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}如此断言的话语必定是谎言
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.62,0:03:38.69,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}百分之几十是自作自受
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.69,0:03:43.60,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}剩下的百分之几不怨任何人 如此不公
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.60,0:03:53.68,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\3c&H1200FF&\t(2560,2810,\3c&H265CF5&)\t(3269,3519,\3c&HDA7B00&)\t(3603,3811,\3c&H47C73E&)\t(3937,4103,\3c&H5F2558&)\t(4437,4562,\3c&H386A2D&)\t(5396,5438,\3c&H1200FF&)\t(6189,6481,\3c&H45B6FE&,\bord0.8)\t(8274,8441,\blur0,\3c&H103568&,\bord2,\1c&HCCE1F4&)\t(8775,9275,\3c&H52164B&)\t(9359,9609,\blur3,\3c&H103568&)}最糟糕的 是自我否定
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.68,0:03:58.68,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}把那个当成我的错吧 把这个也归咎于我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.68,0:04:03.72,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}原谅除我以外的所有人 前进吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.72,0:04:09.29,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}也原谅你自己吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.29,0:04:11.29,op-cn,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.79,0:22:37.09,ed-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}そうじゃない　求めるものは
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.09,0:22:41.62,ed-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}強くコノ手デ掴もう
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.74,0:22:54.27,ed-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}泣いたって変わらないなら
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.27,0:23:00.94,ed-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}戻っても同じ　そう思っていた
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.94,0:23:07.57,ed-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}大事なものが守れないのは
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.57,0:23:14.54,ed-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}弱い僕のせい　そう思っていた
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.54,0:23:20.25,ed-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}どうして今　ここに僕がいる理由は
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.25,0:23:27.30,ed-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}誰が分からなくてもいい　そう　君がいれば
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.30,0:23:34.06,ed-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}見境なく燃える炎を　雲中が指を指す
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.06,0:23:40.69,ed-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}僕はきっと　強くなって　誰だって守り抜く
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.10,0:23:48.77,ed-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\c&HB54E25&\3c&HFFFFFF&}愛したい人の思い　闇をコノ手デ祓おう
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\blur2}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.79,0:22:37.09,ed-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不是这样 我追求的是
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.09,0:22:41.62,ed-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}亲手去紧握
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.74,0:22:54.27,ed-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}一味哭泣 则无法改变
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.27,0:23:00.94,ed-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}回到原点也一样 我如此想到
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.94,0:23:07.57,ed-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}无法保护珍视之人
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.57,0:23:14.54,ed-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是因为我太弱小 我如此想到
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.54,0:23:20.25,ed-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}为什么 我会在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.25,0:23:27.30,ed-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}无人知晓也无妨 只要有你在身旁
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.30,0:23:34.06,ed-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}燃尽万物的烈焰 直冲云霄
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.06,0:23:40.69,ed-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我一定要变强 保护所有人
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.10,0:23:48.77,ed-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\c&HB54E25&\3c&HFFFFFF&\b1}心怀所爱之人 亲手驱散黑暗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.77,0:23:50.77,ed-cn,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.54,0:00:04.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我忍无可忍了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.47,0:00:08.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}这次召集大家不为别的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.11,0:00:13.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}就是为了揪出叛徒
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.70,0:00:17.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}那个时候
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.97,0:00:21.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我看见达摩大人好像在操纵火焰
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.20,0:00:24.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}难道这次的事件是达摩大人…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.69,0:00:29.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}更重要的是 他缺席这次会议不就是证据吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.92,0:00:34.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}等天亮了我一定要去金刚深山找老爸问个清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.15,0:00:50.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}柔造
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.45,0:00:52.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}您辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.86,0:00:58.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}听说今天明陀的干部聚集在一起了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.00,0:01:00.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}出了什么事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.22,0:01:03.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不 有什么传言吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.89,0:01:06.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}那个
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.33,0:01:13.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}所长刚才紧急召集了守卫深部的所有上级驱魔师
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.12,0:01:15.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}所以我们就猜是不是要开会
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.42,0:01:16.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}紧急召集？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.56,0:01:17.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}是的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.68,0:01:18.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.36,0:01:20.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我们也不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.21,0:01:25.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}但是现在放松对深部的警备是不是不太好
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.25,0:01:29.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你说得对 我去问问所长吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.56,0:01:30.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}拜托您了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.23,0:01:45.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}外派所的钥匙？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.09,0:01:49.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}他突然去外派所干嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.76,0:02:18.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.63,0:02:27.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}这是怎么回事 柔造
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.35,0:04:18.65,biaoti,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fax-0.15\fad(0,517)\3c&HC4732D&\pos(352,605)}背信弃义
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.16,0:04:19.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}冷静点
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.86,0:04:22.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}冷静下来想想
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.20,0:04:27.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我太过在意要点燃蜡烛这件事了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.61,0:04:46.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}所以才会把整根蜡烛烧着
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.56,0:04:54.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}真正要点着的是这里
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.89,0:04:54.14,pm1,,0,0,0,,{\pos(242,122)}这 里
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.39,0:04:54.64,pm1,,0,0,0,,{\pos(242,122)}这 里
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.89,0:04:55.14,pm1,,0,0,0,,{\pos(242,122)}这 里
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.80,0:04:59.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}也就是说 只要一点火就够了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.61,0:05:04.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}稍微点一下就行
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.59,0:05:10.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.76,0:05:13.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我做到了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.32,0:05:14.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.76,0:05:17.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我做到了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.37,0:05:18.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}怎么样 修拉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.77,0:05:21.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我点着了 我完美地点着了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.88,0:05:24.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.34,0:05:27.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}终于站上起跑线了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.33,0:05:31.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不会吧 我还没起跑啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.40,0:05:34.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你还必须能随心所欲地操控火焰才行
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.88,0:05:40.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你的火焰要是再失控 可是会被当作驱除对象处死的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.47,0:05:46.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我就开门见山地说了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.54,0:05:49.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}那个恶魔是撒旦之子吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.20,0:05:50.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}正是如此
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.15,0:05:53.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}事到如今也没什么好辩解的了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.75,0:05:57.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你帮助藤本狮郎秘密把他抚养长大 有何目的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.19,0:06:11.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}为了让他成为对抗撒旦的武器
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.08,0:06:14.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}在座的各位
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.39,0:06:16.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}要不要和我打个赌
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.41,0:06:21.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}看看这个撒旦之子会成为虚无界的大魔王
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.20,0:06:26.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}还是会成为骑士团… 不 物质界的救世主
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.35,0:06:27.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}荒谬
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.74,0:06:29.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}他疯了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.28,0:06:31.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}逮捕梅菲斯特
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.71,0:06:33.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}各位
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.67,0:06:39.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}是否接受梅菲斯特·菲雷斯卿的赌约就用投票来决定吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.78,0:06:44.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}首先 他必须通过半年后的驱魔师资格考试
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.40,0:06:47.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}另外 如果他被判断为对物质界有威胁
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.26,0:06:52.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}就要将其作为驱魔对象立刻处刑
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.94,0:06:58.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}可恶 是啊 路还长着啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.81,0:07:04.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}但是这对个人来说只是一小步
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.05,0:07:06.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}对于全人类来说却是一大步
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.73,0:07:10.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你在说什么呢 先冷静下来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.53,0:07:27.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你在这里做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.82,0:07:28.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}蝮
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.71,0:07:39.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}居然是蝮
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.25,0:07:45.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}叛徒果然是你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.89,0:07:50.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}对护摩坛动手脚的也是你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.39,0:07:54.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}审议会的时候你的言辞也很可疑
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.07,0:07:59.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我平常虽然不喜欢你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.25,0:08:02.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}但我觉得你比别人更为明陀着想
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.82,0:08:05.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}可你为什么会做出这种事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.00,0:08:09.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}说话啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.34,0:08:13.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我只是为了让明陀的人清醒过来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.40,0:08:17.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}真正的叛徒是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.23,0:08:21.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}胜吕达摩
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.36,0:08:27.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}还有日本支部长 梅菲斯特·菲雷斯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.38,0:08:29.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}梅菲斯特？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.60,0:08:36.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}梅菲斯特？ 为什么这么说
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.02,0:08:41.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}八年前 我刚进入驱魔塾的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.64,0:08:45.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}藤堂老师告诉了我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.21,0:08:47.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}宝生同学
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.47,0:08:48.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}在
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.58,0:08:54.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}这事你不要说出去 你知道不净王的左眼吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.55,0:09:00.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不净王的左眼是梅菲斯特·菲雷斯支部长的私有物
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.31,0:09:02.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}被寄放在最深部
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.08,0:09:06.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}据说还有一个右眼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.28,0:09:09.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}但还是个谜团
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.12,0:09:12.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你是打倒不净王的明陀家的人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.60,0:09:15.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我以为你会知道些什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.84,0:09:17.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}左眼？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.43,0:09:20.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}还 还有这种东西吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.47,0:09:21.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你 你这是什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.74,0:09:23.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.15,0:09:26.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}那个 那其实是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.24,0:09:32.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}藤堂老师一直对梅菲斯特的行动抱有怀疑
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.86,0:09:35.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}所以打算揭发他的恶行
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.60,0:09:36.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}恶行？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.03,0:09:41.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}而且老师还发现胜吕达摩也牵涉其中
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.23,0:09:46.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}因此我也开始协助藤堂老师
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.45,0:09:48.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}在这几年中彻底调查了一番
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.46,0:09:54.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}虽然一直没有查出决定性的证据
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.39,0:09:55.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}但一周前
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.00,0:09:59.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}在梵蒂冈举行的对梅菲斯特的惩戒审讯中
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.70,0:10:01.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}得到了十分确凿的证据
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.78,0:10:03.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}那就是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.97,0:10:08.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}梅菲斯特没有杀死撒旦之子 还私自将其抚养长大
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.79,0:10:09.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.19,0:10:13.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}而且 为了让那个撒旦之子活下来
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.47,0:10:16.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}还使用了我们明陀的本尊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.67,0:10:21.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你知道这意味着什么吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.09,0:10:27.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}这就是说胜吕达摩和梅菲斯特一起图谋不轨
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.24,0:10:30.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}正如藤堂老师所料
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.59,0:10:34.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}证据呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.11,0:10:37.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}现在这里哪有证据
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.66,0:10:40.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}但这事总有一天会公之于众
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.12,0:10:43.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}唵 婀蜜哩帝 吽 癹吒
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.26,0:10:47.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我们的高层已经不能信任了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.86,0:11:01.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}右眼和左眼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.55,0:11:05.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}都要由藤堂老师封印到比这里更安全的地方去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.18,0:11:06.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}住手 蝮
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.59,0:11:08.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}别擅自行动
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.40,0:11:10.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}至少在大家面前公开把话说清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.15,0:11:17.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}达摩把明陀卖给了正十字骑士团
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.06,0:11:19.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}而上面的人却还一心一意奉他为首领
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.86,0:11:21.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}连父亲大人都是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.82,0:11:24.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}对那些人我要说什么才好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.90,0:11:27.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}志摩家不正是愚忠之首吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.70,0:11:32.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}无论我说什么 他们都只会说「是你想多了」
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.65,0:11:34.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}现在是这样松懈的时候吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.36,0:11:38.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}开始得比想象更快啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.76,0:11:39.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}住持
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.54,0:11:43.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}已经够了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.50,0:11:49.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}那我这就让待机的上级驱魔师部队逮捕她
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.16,0:11:52.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}蟒也同意吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.80,0:11:58.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}蝮已经是成年人了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.61,0:12:00.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.48,0:12:03.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你是认真的吗 蝮
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.44,0:12:06.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我不需要你的理解
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.81,0:12:12.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}这都是为了拯救明陀
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.24,0:12:17.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}那么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.29,0:12:21.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}看在我们自幼相识的份上 就让我来超度你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.50,0:12:23.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}住手 蝮 柔造
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.44,0:12:25.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你们不要自相残杀
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.03,0:12:33.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}怎么了 好像在晃
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.56,0:12:36.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}在那边
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.16,0:12:39.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}外派所好像出了什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.52,0:12:40.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}燐 在这里等着
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.64,0:12:50.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.70,0:12:52.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}喂 别擅自行动
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.40,0:12:54.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}别忘了惩戒审讯时作出的决定
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.83,0:12:56.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.33,0:12:59.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你知道个鬼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.81,0:13:02.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}痛痛痛…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.11,0:13:07.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}但是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.84,0:13:14.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}没办法 跟我来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.77,0:13:24.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}这个晃动不是地震
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.41,0:13:26.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}是入侵者 快到深部去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.00,0:13:28.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}发生什么事了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.99,0:13:30.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}深部出现异常
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.64,0:13:35.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}到底怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.04,0:13:41.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}天花板正在被腐蚀
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.02,0:13:54.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}蝮
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.52,0:14:09.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}志摩同学
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.98,0:14:13.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}好久不见啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.82,0:14:22.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}藤堂
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.57,0:14:23.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你这只老狐狸
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.10,0:14:26.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你欺骗蝮到底有什么企图
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.24,0:14:29.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}老狐狸吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.80,0:14:36.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不错 但是我这次只是协助一下宝生同学而已
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.97,0:14:38.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}正如他所说
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.04,0:14:41.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}和藤堂老师没有关系
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.90,0:14:44.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你被骗了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.64,0:14:48.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你完全被藤堂骗了啊 你知道吗 蝮
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.97,0:14:53.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}住手 你在做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.12,0:14:56.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}住手
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.42,0:15:01.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}被欺骗了的 是你们才对
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.35,0:15:21.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}难道叛徒是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.92,0:15:23.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}竟然是蝮
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.57,0:15:25.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}到底去哪了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.40,0:15:30.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}安静 大家不要慌
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.25,0:15:32.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我们要重整态势
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.38,0:15:42.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}好久不见了 老爸
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.66,0:15:47.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}龙士 好久不见了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.04,0:15:49.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}鸡冠头很不错
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.79,0:15:51.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你要去哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.27,0:15:57.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}虽然很想和你慢慢聊 但我得去追蝮了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.14,0:15:59.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}能不能放开我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.00,0:16:00.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}去追蝮？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.12,0:16:05.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}归根结底 蝮的背叛和这里发生的事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.26,0:16:07.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}这一切不都是你一手造成的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.89,0:16:09.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你不参加会议去做什么了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.71,0:16:10.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}胜吕
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.17,0:16:15.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}那个人是谁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.54,0:16:19.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}胜吕的爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.39,0:16:22.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你说话啊 老爸
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.35,0:16:24.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}就像蝮说的那样 你背叛了我们吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.18,0:16:27.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}怎 怎么可能
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.95,0:16:32.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}既然这样 你就在大家面前把真相说出来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.21,0:16:36.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}真相…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.84,0:16:45.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}那是秘密
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.48,0:16:51.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}即使你是我儿子也不能告诉你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.67,0:16:56.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}都这个时候了 你还在说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.02,0:16:59.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}总之现在要快去追蝮
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.07,0:17:00.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}龙士
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.85,0:17:06.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你要听妈妈和老师的话 别惹事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.40,0:17:07.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}明白了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.00,0:17:09.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}别给我摆父亲架子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.28,0:17:18.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}别总在这种时候摆父亲架子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.56,0:17:22.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我告诉你 你要是不说出来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.53,0:17:25.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}从今往后你就不是我爸了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.52,0:17:32.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}开什么玩笑 你才不是我爸
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.43,0:17:34.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}别在我面前摆父亲架子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.83,0:17:42.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}他是我的儿子 把他还给我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.24,0:17:47.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}老爸
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.00,0:17:52.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}好了 我得走了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.58,0:17:57.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}忍忍吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.11,0:18:04.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.80,0:18:11.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}他什么时候…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.77,0:18:13.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}奥 奥村…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.51,0:18:14.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你为什么要走啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.36,0:18:17.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你是胜吕的爸爸吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.76,0:18:19.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}燐…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.16,0:18:22.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}这样你就高兴了吗 你说啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.16,0:18:26.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}还有你 胜吕
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.14,0:18:28.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你这个混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.16,0:18:30.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}少住持
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.00,0:18:31.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}燐
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.60,0:18:37.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}少住持 你没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.55,0:18:38.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}少住持
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.72,0:18:41.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}刚 刚才是不是有什么闪了一下
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.57,0:18:44.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}虽然不太清楚具体发生了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.75,0:18:48.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}但我先告诉你 你以后一定会后悔的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.22,0:18:51.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}听好了 向老爸道歉 趁现在
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.06,0:18:55.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}和你没关系吧 闭嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.28,0:18:58.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不要轻易和老爸断绝关系
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.23,0:19:00.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我才不想被你教训
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.87,0:19:03.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}好了好了 龙士和燐都别吵了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.13,0:19:05.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}就在这里和好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.24,0:19:08.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你爱去哪去哪
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.11,0:19:11.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不要再回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.91,0:19:35.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}亏我以前还觉得你很帅气
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.08,0:19:34.99,zhu,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}燐
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.50,0:19:38.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我看错你了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.91,0:19:41.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}胜吕
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.75,0:19:42.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}那是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.07,0:19:44.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.04,0:19:46.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}青色的火焰
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.92,0:19:47.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}难道是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.25,0:19:51.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}让一让
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.13,0:19:52.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}住手 燐
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.50,0:20:01.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我又不是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.60,0:20:04.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}唵 巴萨拉 叽尼 哈拉 涅哈他那 娑婆诃
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.73,0:20:11.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}喂 燐 给我老实点
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.15,0:20:16.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我又不是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.56,0:20:21.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}喜欢撒旦才当他儿子的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.48,0:20:24.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}但是你不一样
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.52,0:20:26.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你不一样吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.66,0:20:30.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}跟老爸道歉 等他死了可就晚了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.23,0:20:35.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}别像我一样
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.10,0:20:38.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}现在马上跟老爸道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.47,0:20:43.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}少住持
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.76,0:20:48.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}柔造
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.29,0:20:52.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}抱歉擅自插手 但请先逃离这里
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.12,0:20:58.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}梅菲斯特没有杀死撒旦之子 还私自将其抚养长大
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.12,0:21:00.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}就是这个孩子吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.36,0:21:05.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}没想到廉造的朋友竟然是撒旦之子
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.23,0:21:11.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}唵 嘛呢 叭哒 吽
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.23,0:21:11.72,zhu,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}注：六字大明咒
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.85,0:21:20.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}燐 冷静一点
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.74,0:21:23.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你忘记惩戒审讯时定下的条件了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.72,0:21:29.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}放出火焰的话就会被当作驱魔对象处死了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.38,0:21:30.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我正在…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.30,0:21:34.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}说很重要的话
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.72,0:21:37.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}别妨碍我 母猪
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.80,0:21:41.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}母猪？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.06,0:21:54.47,zhu,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}唵 佉契佉契 佉比契著央著 吒契婆那 娑婆诃
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.09,0:21:50.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}这到底是…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.17,0:21:58.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}燐 燐
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.36,0:21:59.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}真是笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.38,0:22:04.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}谁来帮个忙把他隔离起来
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.42,0:22:06.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}他已经晕过去了 没事的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.24,0:22:09.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}雾隐队长
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.80,0:22:14.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}所长 引起这么大的骚动真是非常抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.13,0:22:18.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}这件事你稍后应该会解释清楚吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.99,0:22:20.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}是的 当然
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.35,0:22:22.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}燐
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.22,0:22:24.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}燐
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.75,0:24:05.42,zhu,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}第五集 一缘一会
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.48,0:24:10.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}对你来说可能负担还是太大了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.06,0:24:12.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}替我向燐问好
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.21,0:24:14.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}毒性更猛烈的瘴气
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.32,0:24:16.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}难道藤堂的目的是…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.04,0:24:19.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}放出火焰被大家看到了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.44,0:24:20.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}那个笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.03,0:24:23.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你看着吧 藤本
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.89,0:24:25.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}
